ight on issues that continue to dominate the controversy surrounding homeopathy to this very day.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aAlternative medicinezGermanyxHistory. 0aHomeopathyzGermanyxHistory. 0aRomanticismzGermany. 7aMEDICAL / History.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311066594940uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978148751263740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781487512637423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781487512637.jpg  a978-3-11-066594-9  University of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles